<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Bus Product</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/public/favicon.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="dashboard layout">
    <%- include("partials/sidebar", { active }) %>

    <section class="content" data-menti-ocr="1">
      <header class="page-header">
        <div class="page-title">
          <h1>
            <span class="page-title-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M5 12a7 7 0 0 1 7-7h5a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-5a7 7 0 0 1-7-7z"></path>
                <path d="M9 10h6"></path>
                <path d="M9 14h4"></path>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Menti</span>
          </h1>
          <p>Menti ekranini uygulama icinde ac. Sol panelden ekran goruntusu yukleyip OCR ile metin cikar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="page-actions">
          <div class="user-pill"><%= user.displayName %></div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="menti-layout">
        <aside class="table-card panel-card menti-ocr-card">
          <div class="menti-ocr-header">
            <div>
              <h2>OCR Araci</h2>
              <p class="muted">Ekran goruntusu secin veya bu sayfaya yapistirin. Metin bu panelde cikarilir.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="pill muted" data-menti-ocr-status-pill="1">Hazir</span>
          </div>

          <div class="menti-frame-note inline-alert">
            Menti iframe icerigi dogrudan okunamaz. Bu yuzden ekran goruntusu yukleyip OCR calistirabilirsiniz.
          </div>

          <label class="menti-ocr-dropzone" data-menti-ocr-dropzone="1">
            <input type="file" accept="image/*" data-menti-ocr-input="1" hidden />
            <span class="menti-ocr-dropzone-title">Gorsel Sec veya Ctrl+V ile Yapistir</span>
            <span class="menti-ocr-dropzone-subtitle">PNG, JPG, WEBP veya ekran goruntusu kabul edilir.</span>
          </label>

          <div class="menti-ocr-actions">
            <button type="button" data-menti-ocr-run="1" disabled>Metni Cikar</button>
            <button type="button" class="ghost" data-menti-ocr-copy="1" disabled>Metni Kopyala</button>
            <button type="button" class="ghost" data-menti-ocr-clear="1" disabled>Temizle</button>
          </div>

          <div class="menti-ocr-status" data-menti-ocr-status="1">
            Gorsel bekleniyor.
          </div>

          <div class="menti-ocr-preview-wrap" data-menti-ocr-preview-wrap="1" hidden>
            <img class="menti-ocr-preview" data-menti-ocr-preview="1" alt="OCR gorsel onizleme" />
          </div>

          <label class="menti-notes-field">
            <span>Cikarilan Metin</span>
            <textarea
              rows="12"
              data-menti-ocr-output="1"
              placeholder="OCR sonucu burada gorunecek"
            ></textarea>
          </label>

          <div class="menti-ocr-hint">
            <strong>Ipucu:</strong> Soruyu daha net almak icin ekran goruntusunu crop edip tekrar yukleyin.
          </div>
        </aside>

        <section class="table-card panel-card menti-browser-card">
          <div class="menti-browser-toolbar">
            <div class="menti-browser-address" aria-label="Menti adresi">
              <span class="menti-browser-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span><%= mentiUrl %></span>
            </div>
            <a class="button-link ghost" href="<%= mentiUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              Yeni Sekmede Ac
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="menti-frame-note inline-alert">
            Gorsel yakalamak icin Menti ekranindan ekran goruntusu alip soldaki OCR aracina yukleyin.
          </div>

          <div class="menti-browser-frame-wrap">
            <iframe
              class="menti-browser-frame"
              src="<%= mentiUrl %>"
              title="Menti"
              referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
              loading="eager"
              allow="clipboard-read; clipboard-write"
              data-menti-frame="1"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </section>
      </section>
    </section>
    <script src="/public/app.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
